show.description: My CEO made me Pregnant is a high-stakes romantic drama where powerful secrets, betrayal, and hidden identities collide as Leena, a brilliant tech genius, fights to reclaim her place and protect her unborn child. Amidst corporate wars and emotional chaos, she must expose lies, survive conspiracies, and stand against the man she once loved.
